title: GET_VEHICLE_WHEEL_SURFACE_MATERIAL
content:
0xA7F04022// GetVehicleWheelSurfaceMaterial
int GET_VEHICLE_WHEEL_SURFACE_MATERIAL(Vehicle vehicle, int wheelIndex);Parameters:vehicle: The vehicle to obtain data for.wheelIndex: Index of wheel, 0-3.Returns: Integer representing the index of the current surface material of that wheel. Check materials.dat for the indexes.
